        -- Posted by robin on 11:05 am on July 24, 2001<p>
        Our last vacation was to San Diego to visit family. &nbsp;Robin loved the beach and we ended up going every day! &nbsp;They have 'Dog Beach' in Ocean Beach, Fiesta Island in Mission Bay and a few others we didn't get to that are all off leash. &nbsp;Along the way we stopped at the Virgin River Casino for the night, it was the most dog friendly motel we've stayed at, and very cheap too. <br>We'd like to take more fun trips with our dog, any suggestions?

        <p><p>
        
        <p>
