        -- Posted by Cynthia Blue on 9:30 am on Aug. 8, 2001<p>
        That sounds like fun. I definitely want to take my dogs to the beach sometime... though encouraging them to like the water a bit more first would probably be a good idea. &nbsp;:) <br> <br>We are going to Coyotte Buttes in September, a place in Southern Utah which is supposed to be very beautiful. &nbsp;It's reservation only and you can make them 6 months in advance. I hope to take some pictures while there and post them up on the web. &nbsp;Do you have any beach pictures?

